name: Aozora (青空)
description:
(n) blue sky.

Jakarta has a poor level of air quality. Based on iqair.com, which ranks air quality around the world, on September 17, 2021, Jakarta is ranked 3rd in the world with the worst air quality.

This photo was taken when Jakarta was in a state of lockdown due to the pandemic. When most people stay at home.

Hopefully the pandemic is coming to an end and the air quality in Jakarta is getting better.
